.hero-unit
  :markdown
    #### This project is bootstrapped!

:markdown
  ## Setup
  
  Now setup your blog as described in [the middleman blogging extension documentation](http://middlemanapp.com/extensions/blog/) 
  
  ### Views &amp; Layouts

  Your source files are stored in the &lt;kbd&gt;source&lt;/kbd&gt; folder. The main layout
  file for this project is &lt;kbd&gt;source/layout.haml&lt;/kbd&gt;.

:markdown
  ### Stylesheets, Sass &amp;amp; Compass

  This project is pre-configured for [Sass](http://sass-lang.com) and
  [Compass](http://compass-style.org). Store your &lt;kbd&gt;sass&lt;/kbd&gt; and
  &lt;kbd&gt;scss&lt;/kbd&gt; files in the &lt;kbd&gt;source/stylesheets&lt;/kbd&gt; directory.

  Twitter bootstrap styles are pulled in via the [bootstrap-sass](https://github.com/thomas-mcdonald/bootstrap-sass)
  gem.
  
  The &lt;kbd&gt;source/stylesheets/screen.css.sass&lt;/kbd&gt; stylesheet shows how to customise twitter bootstrap
  styles using the variables that are provided for precisely this purpose. 

  
